@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Translate (auto-detect source language)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/translate
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-Id: demo-auto-detect-001

{
  "text": "Bonjour tout le monde!",
  "targetLang": "en"
}

### Translate (explicit source language)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/translate
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-Id: demo-explicit-001

{
  "text": "Guten Morgen, wie geht's?",
  "sourceLang": "de",
  "targetLang": "en"
}

### Translate (multi-line content, preserve line breaks)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/translate
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-Id: demo-multiline-001

{
  "text": "Line 1: Hello\nLine 2: This is a test.\n{name} should remain as a placeholder.",
  "sourceLang": "en",
  "targetLang": "ja"
}